original: Brenke, Eskil Gottfrid, civilingenjör, Nässjö, f. 15/12/06 i Säby, Jönköp. 1. G. 36 m. Margit Kjellin. B’arn: Christer f. 39, UMa-Briitt 44. — Stud:ex. i Eksjö 26, avg:ex. fr. KTH (E) 33. Anst. v. Smål. Kraft A-B i Nässjö 33-34, v. SJs elektrifier. i Näs’sjö 35-36, bitr. ing. v. Nässjö stads elverk 35-36, driftsing. v. Smålands Kraft A-B sed. 36. Suppl. i styr. Led. av brandstyr. Led. av Sv. tekn:-fören. fr. 34, medl. av KFUM. Hob-bie’s: arbetet, friluftsliv.
translated: Brenke, Eskil Gottfrid, civil engineer, Nässjö, born December 15, 1906 in Säby, Jönköping. Married once in 1936 to Margit Kjellin. Children: Christer, born in 1939, and UMa-Briitt, born in 1944. Graduated from Eksjö in 1926 and KTH (E) in 1933. Employed by Smål. Kraft A-B in Nässjö from 1933-34, assisted with electrification of SJs in Nässjö from 1935-36, assistant engineer at Nässjö city power plant from 1935-36, and then chief engineer of Smålands Kraft A-B since 1936. Serves as a member of the fire department board and the Swedish Technical Association since 1934, and is a member of KFUM. Hobbies include work and outdoor activities.
